1. INTRODUCTION\par
Car and bus travel agencies need an effective management platform for handling their respective transportation services. The existing system relies on manual data recording for management which is very tedious and time-consuming, involving a lot of manpower and paperwork. So, the current system needs to be computerized and web-based.This project aims at offering the best of cab services to clients in need. It has a fleet of cabs ranging from normal budget cabs to expensive luxury cabs. A good feature of a web-based system such as this is that it offers online cab hire for corporate houses. This makes the overall car service work easily accessible for all and reliable as well.\par
1.1 Purpose\par
The purpose of this document is to build an online system to manage cabs and customers to ease the cab management.The cab  management system is to ease cab management and to create a convenient and easy-to-use application for passengers, trying to easily book the cab. The system is based on a relational database with its cab management and booking functions  \par
1.2 Project Scope \par
The system ensures that the users can book the cab as per their requirements by logging on to the website. It allows users to book their cabs online, manage their bookings and cancel their bookings at any point of time. Regular updates are provided to the customer so that they are aware of their bookings, driver details, and booking status. The user can also drop in their suggestions or queries in the feedback form.\par
